description: Welcome to Southie! Presenting a spacious 2BD/2BA corner unit on the East Side delivered with hardwood floors & high ceilings throughout, recessed lighting and a gas fireplace. The grand open living & dining area leads to a private deck, perfect for entertaining, and beyond an oversized island the ultra-modern kitchen provides abundant cabinet storage, granite countertops, a 6-burner gas range and a designer tile backsplash. The master bedroom includes an en-suite bath with double vanity and a glass-enclosed shower; both bedrooms offer generous closet space with California Closet systems. Additional modern comforts include in-unit laundry, central A/C, surround sound PLUS a separate storage locker. This young 20-unit development in a professionally managed elevator building includes a climate-controlled parking garage with direct access. Close proximity to local grocery and many dining & social establishments along East Broadway with convenient commuter options via MBTA bus lines and on/off ramps to both 93 & MA Pike.
